{"ja491:0.1":"Jataka ","ja491:0.2":"Pakinnakanipata ","ja491:0.3":"Salikedaravagga ","ja491:0.4":"8. Mahamorajataka ","ja491:1.1":"“Sace hi tyaham dhanahetu gahito, ","ja491:1.2":"Ma mam vadhi jivagaham gahetva; ","ja491:1.3":"Ranno ca mam samma upantikam nehi, ","ja491:1.4":"Manne dhanam lacchasinapparupam”. ","ja491:2.1":"“Na me ayam tuyha vadhaya ajja, ","ja491:2.2":"Samahito capadhure khurappo; ","ja491:2.3":"Pasanca tyaham adhipatayissam, ","ja491:2.4":"Yathasukham gacchatu moraraja”. ","ja491:3.1":"“Yam satta vassani mamanubandhi, ","ja491:3.2":"Rattindivam khuppipasam sahanto; ","ja491:3.3":"Atha kissa mam pasavasupanitam, ","ja491:3.4":"Pamuttave icchasi bandhanasma. ","ja491:4.1":"Panatipata virato nusajja, ","ja491:4.2":"Abhayam nu te sabbabhutesu dinnam; ","ja491:4.3":"Yam mam tuvam pasavasupanitam, ","ja491:4.4":"Pamuttave icchasi bandhanasma”. ","ja491:5.1":"“Panatipata viratassa bruhi, ","ja491:5.2":"Abhayanca yo sabbabhutesu deti; ","ja491:5.3":"Pucchami tam morarajetamattham, ","ja491:5.4":"Ito cuto kim labhate sukham so”. ","ja491:6.1":"“Panatipata viratassa brumi, ","ja491:6.2":"Abhayanca yo sabbabhutesu deti; ","ja491:6.3":"Dittheva dhamme labhate pasamsam, ","ja491:6.4":"Sagganca so yati sarirabheda”. ","ja491:7.1":"“Na santi deva iti ahu eke, ","ja491:7.2":"Idheva jivo vibhavam upeti; ","ja491:7.3":"Tatha phalam sukatadukkatanam, ","ja491:7.4":"Dattupannattanca vadanti danam; ","ja491:7.5":"Tesam vaco arahatam saddahano, ","ja491:7.6":"Tasma aham sakune badhayami”. ","ja491:8.1":"“Cando ca suriyo ca ubho sudassana, ","ja491:8.2":"Gacchanti obhasayamantalikkhe; ","ja491:8.3":"Imassa lokassa parassa va te, ","ja491:8.4":"Katham nu te ahu manussaloke”. ","ja491:9.1":"“Cando ca suriyo ca ubho sudassana, ","ja491:9.2":"Gacchanti obhasayamantalikkhe; ","ja491:9.3":"Parassa lokassa na te imassa, ","ja491:9.4":"Devati te ahu manussaloke”. ","ja491:10.1":"“Ettheva te nihata hinavada, ","ja491:10.2":"Ahetuka ye na vadanti kammam; ","ja491:10.3":"Tatha phalam sukatadukkatanam, ","ja491:10.4":"Dattupannattam ye ca vadanti danam”. ","ja491:11.1":"“Addha hi saccam vacanam tavedam, ","ja491:11.2":"Kathanhi danam aphalam bhaveyya; ","ja491:11.3":"Tatha phalam sukatadukkatanam, ","ja491:11.4":"Dattupannattanca katham bhaveyya. ","ja491:12.1":"Kathankaro kintikaro kimacaram, ","ja491:12.2":"Kim sevamano kena tapogunena; ","ja491:12.3":"Akkhahi me morarajetamattham, ","ja491:12.4":"Yatha aham no nirayam pateyyam”. ","ja491:13.1":"“Ye keci atthi samana pathabya, ","ja491:13.2":"Kasayavattha anagariya te; ","ja491:13.3":"Patova pindaya caranti kale, ","ja491:13.4":"Vikalacariya virata hi santo. ","ja491:14.1":"Te tattha kalenupasankamitva, ","ja491:14.2":"Pucchahi yam te manaso piyam siya; ","ja491:14.3":"Te te pavakkhanti yathapajanam, ","ja491:14.4":"Imassa lokassa parassa cattham”. ","ja491:15.1":"“Tacamva jinnam urago puranam, ","ja491:15.2":"Pandupalasam harito dumova; ","ja491:15.3":"Esappahino mama luddabhavo, ","ja491:15.4":"Jahamaham luddakabhavamajja. ","ja491:16.1":"Ye capi me sakuna atthi baddha, ","ja491:16.2":"Sataninekani nivesanasmim; ","ja491:16.3":"Tesampaham jivitamajja dammi, ","ja491:16.4":"Mokkhanca te patta sakam niketam”. ","ja491:17.1":"“Luddo cari pasahattho aranne, ","ja491:17.2":"Badhetu moradhipatim yasassim; ","ja491:17.3":"Bandhitva moradhipatim yasassim, ","ja491:17.4":"Dukkha sa pamucci yathaham pamutto”ti. ","ja491:18.1":"Mahamorajatakam atthamam. "}